task.summary: Update @author on all classes and reformat whole project
Added missing instructions (sub, mul, div, out, bnz) and respective basic tests
Replace instantiation by name with reflection
Create an instance of "mul" just with reflection
Use reflection to translate all instructions
Refactor code to take advantage of lombok, but because it doesn't work well with super() also refactored the abstract class Instruction to be an interface.
Extract getInstruction() logic from the translator into a specialised Instruction factory.
Reduce boiler plate in the Translator; use hasNextLine() instead of exception handling; use split() instead of customised scanning functions.
Add support to configure the instruction class for an opcode without recompiling.
Add support to configure the instruction class for an opcode without recompiling.
Improved the instruction factory and added tests for all instructions.
